<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Four <rs type="material" key="marmor">blue marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">column</rs>s; i. Broken above and below (<measure dim="diameter">0.48</measure>); ii. Broken above, moulding survives below (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">c. 0.83</measure>); surface damaged. iii. Fragment broken on all sides (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.40</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.355</measure>); iv. broken column drum of <rs type="material" key="marmor">blueish white marble</rs> (<measure dim="diameter">0.46</measure>; total height not reliably measurable).</p>
</div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p>ii. Inscribed just above (c. 0.07) moulding; iv. inscribed at about 1.60 from base of column.</p></div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Neat capitals with restrained seriphs, <measure precision="circa" type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">monument</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
